On Ubuntu, run the following:
-------------------------------------------------------------
$ CXXFLAGS="-Wall -g -O3 -march=corei7" ./configure --prefix=/usr --libdir=/usr/lib --with-boost-libdir=/usr/lib/x86_64-linux-gnu


On Fedore based systems:
------------------------------------------------------------
$ CXXFLAGS="-Wall -g -O3 -march=corei7" ./configure --prefix=/usr --libdir=/usr/lib64 


The above is just an example, and you can change the flags as you like. (e.g. change optimization flags)
